      "pid": 97, "iso_pid": 62561,
      "name": "Demanded Engine - Percent Torque", "name_zh": "需求发动机扭矩百分比",
      "description": "Driver-demanded engine percent torque. Ranges from -125% (e.g., engine braking/coast-down) to +130% of reference torque (PID $63). Includes requested torque from all sources (driver, cruise control, traction control).",
      "description_zh": "驾驶员需求的发动机扭矩百分比。范围-125%(如发动机制动/滑行)至+130%参考扭矩(PID $63)。包含所有来源的扭矩需求(驾驶员、巡航、牵引力控制)。",
      "type": "numeric", "data_bytes": 1,
      "items": [{ "label": "TQ_DD", "bytes": "A", "formula": "A - 125", "unit": "%", "min": -125, "max": 130 }]
    },
    {
      "pid": 98, "iso_pid": 62562,
      "name": "Actual Engine - Percent Torque", "name_zh": "实际发动机扭矩百分比",
      "description": "Actual engine output percent torque (indicated torque minus friction/pumping losses). Percent of reference torque (PID $63). Negative values indicate motoring (friction + pumping > combustion).",
      "description_zh": "实际发动机输出扭矩百分比(指示扭矩减去摩擦/泵送损失)。参考扭矩(PID $63)的百分比。负值表示拖动(摩擦+泵送>燃烧)。",
      "type": "numeric", "data_bytes": 1,
      "items": [{ "label": "TQ_ACT", "bytes": "A", "formula": "A - 125", "unit": "%", "min": -125, "max": 130 }]
    },
    {
      "pid": 99, "iso_pid": 62563,
      "name": "Engine Reference Torque", "name_zh": "发动机参考扭矩",
      "description": "Engine reference torque in Nm. The 100% point for PID $61/$62/$64/$8E. Typically the maximum rated torque of the engine. Shall not change while the engine is running.",
      "description_zh": "发动机参考扭矩(Nm)。PID $61/$62/$64/$8E的100%基准点。通常为发动机最大额定扭矩。发动机运行时不应改变。",
